Our Company


Delivering the connected world





 






We help people, businesses and things communicate better.The digital world promises consumers a better, more connected life, and we’re the ones delivering it. We make it possible for people to stay in touch and businesses to connect with their customers. We’re also bringing technology and hands-on learning opportunities directly to kids who need it most. Our goal is to inspire tomorrow’s creators to use technology to build brighter futures for themselves, their families and the world.
What we do






 








U.S. coverage98%wireless network coverage 










Broadband100%fiber optic network 










Video & Advertising150Mhours of video streamed monthly 










Internet of Things14K+developers hosted on ThingSpace 










Security200+data centers in 24 countries 



















 

 



Innovating for tomorrowOur network technologies are empowering entrepreneurs and businesses to quickly bring big, bold ideas to market.
