^ http://www1.salary.com/Lowell-C-McAdam-Salary-Bonus-Stock-Options-for-VERIZON-COMMUNICATIONS-INC.html
^ U.S. Public Records Index Vols. 1 & 2 (Provo, UT: Ancestry.com Operations, Inc.), 2011.
